'''浓湿雾'''（{{lang-es|Garúa|translation=[[毛毛雨|毛毛雨]]}}）是[[南美洲|南美洲]]的一种天气现象，常在南半球的冬季发生于[[秘鲁|秘鲁]]、[[厄瓜多尔|厄瓜多尔]]南部和[[智利|智利]]北部沿岸。热带海岸沙漠受浓湿雾影响，温度适中、湿度偏大。浓湿雾为干燥地区带来大量水气，并保证{{le|雾植|lomas}}的生存。浓湿雾因其发生率和持续性以及对气候和环境的影响，而在众多天气现象中显得特别。

== 浓湿雾的形成 ==
[[File:Reserva_Nacional_Lomas_de_Lachay,_Huaral,_Lima,_Perú_01.jpg|thumb]]
[[秘鲁涼流|秘鲁涼流]]对南纬5度至30度之间的秘鲁和智利沿岸浓湿雾的形成起重要的作用。在这个长达2800米的范围内，洋流为常年干旱地区带来丰沛的水汽，令气候变得温和。同时，该地区会产生[[逆温|逆温]]现象，气温随着高度的上升而上升，临近洋面的气温反而较低。冷空气借由[[信风|信风]]向东吹至岸边，雾气冷凝形成浓湿雾的景象。<ref name=":1">{{Cite journal|title=Re-evaluating the resource potential of lomas fog oasis environments for Preceramic hunter-gatherers under past-ENSO modeson the south coast of Peru|author=Beresford-Jones, David et al|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0277379115301463|journal=Quaternary Science Reviews|issue=|doi=|others=|year=2015|volume=129|page=198|pmid=|access-date=2020-07-29|archive-date=2021-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210909044424/https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0277379115301463|dead-url=no}}</ref>

尽管名为“[[霧|雾]]”，但浓湿雾并不会转化为[[雨|降雨]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Driest Place on Earth|url=https://www.nationalgeographic.com/magazine/|accessdate=2020-07-29|author=Vesilind, Priit J.|date=2003|format=|work=National Geographic Magazine|publisher=|language=en|archive-url=https://archive.today/20120629025350/http://ngm.nationalgeographic.com/ngm/0602/feature1/text4.html|archive-date=2012-06-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>浓湿雾中的水滴直径为1～40微米，不足以形成雨水。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=How Chile's fogcatchers are bringing water to the driest desert on Earth|url=https://newatlas.com/how-the-fogcatchers-of-the-atacama-are-bringing-water-to-the-driest-desert-on-earth/39040/|accessdate=2020-07-29|author=Lavars, Nick|date=2015-08-25|format=|work=New Atlas|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200527095310/https://newatlas.com/how-the-fogcatchers-of-the-atacama-are-bringing-water-to-the-driest-desert-on-earth/39040/|archive-date=2020-05-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>
